<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay frames="40" />
名為捕蟲大會的戰爭，<delay20 />
就要在<tag a="110" b="8" /><delay8 /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />展開了呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你想問對手是誰？<10_4 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對手不是別人，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />正是你自己啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然統一稱為昆蟲，<delay20 />
但其中還分為有六隻腳的甲蟲<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有八隻腳的蜘蛛類<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />以及有30～50隻腳的多足類，<delay20 />
種類可是多的很呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總覺得不管是哪一種昆蟲，<delay20 />
都有很多隻腳呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所謂的捕蟲，<delay20 />
就像談戀愛時的應對進退一樣！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果不加思索就隨意靠近，<delay20 />
目標馬上就會逃走的，<delay20 />
所以要拿起捕蟲網，慢慢接近。<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就這樣一步一步地接近昆蟲，<delay20 />
直到觸手可及<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是該揮下捕蟲網的時候了！<pageBreak /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒錯，就像談戀愛一樣<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也會有失敗的時候就是了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哈哈～！</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />參加捕蟲大會時，<delay20 />
得在時間限制內
抓到越多昆蟲越好！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />換句話說，<delay8 />
就算帶著一大堆事先抓到的昆蟲來參加，<delay20 />
也是沒有意義的喔。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果想參加捕蟲大會的話，<delay20 />
只要去廣場<delay8 />找<colour id="3" />龍克斯<colour id="65535" />說話就行了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />我嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我就不參加了。<delay20 />
昆蟲對我來說<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />長得有點太嚇人了。</message>
</msbt>